Koor, Property & Building in Talks on Terms of NYC Building Deal

-- B y   S h o s h a n n a   S o l o m o n
-- 
2011-10-09T06:28:40Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-09/koor-property-building-in-talks-on-terms-of-nyc-building-deal.html
Koor Industries Ltd. (KOR)  said it was in
talks with Property and Building Corp. to change the terms of a
deal for the HSBC building in  New York City , according to a
statement filed on Oct. 6 with the Tel Aviv Stock Exchange.  In September Koor agreed to sell a 50 percent stake in the
HSBC property to Property and Building for approximately $138
million.  .  To contact the reporter on this story:
Shoshanna Solomon in Tel Aviv at 
 ssolomon22@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Calev Ben-David at 
 cbendavid@bloomberg.net  